title: Karan Johar & Alia Bhatt interview with Rajeev Masand I Lockdown I Takht
description: In this interview with Rajeev Masand, filmmaker #KaranJohar talks about the current scenario and how it has led to uncertainty within Bollywood about the future of unreleased and in-production films. Karan explains how he is using this time to fine-tune the script of his next film #Takht whose shooting was originally meant to begin in April. They are joined on the call by #AliaBhatt who reveals what she has been keeping herself busy with while grounded indoors, and how she is wrapping her head around the realisation that it may be impossible to plan ahead at this point.
